\pard\sb480\sa200\cf4\b\fs40 1. Executive Summary\par

\pard\sa140\sl360\slmult1\cf3\b0\fs22 VoteSphere is a multi-tenant, cloud-native digital voting platform purpose-built for secondary schools (SHS) and universities across West Africa and beyond. It replaces manual paper balloting and fragmented spreadsheet-based vote counting with a secure, auditable, and accessible system that works on every device \f2\emdash\f0  including feature phones via USSD.\cf0\par

\pard\sa100\par

\pard\sa140\sl360\slmult1\cf3 The platform is owned and operated by a single platform owner (you) who licenses access to individual institutions. Each institution gets an isolated environment, branded sub-domain, and tailored subscription plan. Revenue is generated through subscriptions, per-transaction fees, and premium add-ons \f2\emdash\f0  all configurable from the owner's monetization dashboard.\cf0\par

